#

Zucchini Fritters with Tzatziki Sauce

35 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow Carb

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthySnack

Description

Crispy on the outside, soft on the inside, these zucchini fritters are a delightful snack or side dish, paired with a refreshing tzatziki sauce.

Ingredients

  • zucchini: 2 medium
  • eggs: 2
  • all-purpose flour: 1/2 cup
  • grated parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • olive oil: for frying
  • greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1/2 (grated and drained)
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • fresh dill: 1 tablespoon (chopped)
  • garlic (minced): 1 clove
